        "pf_3286277d_value": "\"I've had massive acne and pimples since I was 13. Tried a bunch of stuff but nothing works. Been using Klyr for a few weeks now and honestly it's not visible that I wear something PLUS my skin just looks calmer and the breakouts aren’t as crazy anymore. Pretty happy with it so far.\"",
        "pf_4a079caa_value": "Concealing Cream+ is for anyone who wants to instantly look fresher. Whether you’ve got an important meeting or a sudden breakout, it adapts to your skin tone for a seamless, invisible finish. If you want a fast, effective fix for skin imperfections, this is it.",
        "pf_35dde10b_value": "You’ve tried everything – creams, serums, harsh treatments – nothing made a real difference.Then you discover Klyr: a unique blend of instant results and long-term skin benefits. Lightweight, invisible, and genuinely good for your skin.",
