        "pf_e45fd9e2_value": "Men try countless creams, serums, and treatments, yet <strong>nothing truly fixes the visible issues</strong> - the dark circles, sudden breakouts, or persistent redness.<strong><br></strong>",
        "pf_758905ae_value": "Traditional make-up is thick, shiny, and designed for a completely different skin type. On men, it’s noticeable, <strong>heavy, and uncomfortable</strong>.<strong><br></strong>",
